Without prejudice to the generality of the provision contained in section 37 of this act, the chairperson of the Dzongkhag Disaster Management committee shall:
* regularly review and assess the effectiveness of Dzongkhag Disaster Management and contingency Plan;
* ensure decision and policy formulated by the Dzongkhag Disaster Management committee is implemented;
* ensure that disaster risk reduction and disaster management activities are consistent with Disaster Management strategic Policy framework;
* Provide prompt information on a disaster or an impending disaster situation to the Department of Disaster Management;
* Provide regular updates and detailed reports on a disaster

